@startuml
' 全局样式配置
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 60

title C4 架构容器图示例 - 当前 RISC-V 模拟器宏观架构

actor "开发与验证人员" as Developer

package "Model Simulator (src/)" {
    [src/simulation (仿真框架)] as SimApp
    
    [src/core (核心时序)] as Core
    [src/uncore (非核心时序)] as Uncore
    [src/funcmodel (功能模型库)] as FuncModel
    [src/basic (基础数据结构)] as Basic
    [src/utility (公共工具与日志)] as Utility
}

[mavis (外部译码库)] as Mavis

Developer -down-> SimApp : 发起任务

SimApp -down-> Core : 驱动时钟
note on link: 驱动前端/后端时钟

SimApp -down-> Uncore : 驱动时钟
note on link: 驱动 Cache/NoC 时钟

SimApp -down-> Mavis : 挂载译码

Core -down-> FuncModel : 调用功能状态
Uncore -down-> FuncModel : 调用 Cache 功能

Core -down-> Basic : 流转 Inst
Uncore -down-> Basic : 流转 MemAccessInfo

Core -right-> Utility : 调用插件
note on link: 注入日志输出与观测插件

note right of SimApp
  展示当前 src/ 目录下各个核心大模块
  之间错综复杂的真实调用与依赖关系。
end note
@enduml
